      <br>• Easier to hire experienced drivers: premium attracts talent
      <br>• Driver productivity: 10-15% higher (less fatigue, better comfort)</p>

      <p><strong>Cost of Driver Turnover:</strong>
      <br>• Recruiting new driver: RM2,000 - RM3,000
      <br>• Training period: 2-4 weeks reduced productivity
      <br>• Lost revenue: RM10,000 - RM20,000 per turnover
      <br><strong>Annual Savings (30% less turnover):</strong> RM15,000 - RM25,000</p>

